es.ull.iis.simulation.core
Interface Resource

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<SimulationObject>, Describable, Identifiable, SimulationObject, VariableStore, VariableStoreSimulationObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
Resource, Resource
public interface Resource
extends VariableStoreSimulationObject, Describable

A simulation resource whose availability is controlled by means of timetable entries. A timetable entry us a trio <ResourceType, SimulationCycle, long> which defines a resource type, an availability cycle, and the duration of each availability period. Timetable entries can be overlapped in time, thus allowing the resource for being potentially available for different resource types simultaneously. A resource finishes its execution when it has no longer valid timetable entries.

Author:
Iván Castilla Rodríguez
